        "class": "ital",
        "text": "Them that hate him — ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "Not only those who hate him directly and properly, (for so did few or none of the Israelites to whom he here speaks,) but those who hate him by implication and consequence; those who hate and oppose his people and word; those who wilfully persist in the breach of his commandments. ",
        "children": []
