      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "To their face — ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "That is, openly, and so as they shall see it, and not be able to avoid it. ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "Slack — ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "So as to delay it beyond the fit time or season for vengeance, yet withal he is long-suffering, and slow to anger.",
